OL,3,CSupport for struggling Derby families
OL,4,Cthis winter after cost of living boost
OL,6,FStruggling Derby families are set to
OL,7,Fget vital support this winter after
OL,8,Fthe city was given a #2 million cost
OL,9,Fof living boost.
OL,11,FDerby City Council's Labour cabinet
OL,12,Fhas approved a #2.25 million grant
OL,13,Ffrom the Government to allow it to
OL,14,Fextend its Household Support Fund.
OL,16,FIt has supported thousands of families
OL,17,Fin the city during recent years `
OL,18,Fproviding them with free food vouchers
OL,19,Fduring school term breaks and energy
OL,20,Fbill support during the cost of living
OL,21,Fcrisis.
