OL,6,FThe money is allocated to local
OL,7,Fauthorities from the central
OL,8,Fgovernment. This has been the case
OL,9,Fsince the fund was launched in 2021.
OL,11,FIn the March 2024 budget, announced by
OL,12,Fthe previous Conservative government,
OL,13,Fit was announced that the fund would
OL,14,Fcontinue until September ` triggering
OL,15,Fconcern about whether it would
OL,16,Fcontinue in the long term.
