OL,4,Cthis winter after cost of living boost
OL,6,FBut council papers state the new
OL,7,FLabour government has announced a six-
OL,8,Fmonth extension to the Household
OL,9,FSupport Fund to run from October 2024
OL,10,Fto March 2025.
OL,12,FThe government has allocated
OL,13,F#2.25million to Derby City Council. It
OL,14,Fis set to benefit struggling Derby
OL,15,Fresidents by:
OL,17,FDerby City Council has been praised by
OL,18,Fthe government for how well it has
OL,19,Fused the Household Support Fund in
OL,20,Frecent years.
