OL,7,FWork and Pensions said the council's
OL,8,Fstrategic use of the cash pot "serves
OL,9,Fas a model for addressing poverty and
OL,10,Fdeprivation".
OL,12,FBefore a cabinet meeting held earlier
OL,13,Fthis month, councillor Sarah Chambers,
OL,14,Fcabinet member for cost of living,
OL,15,Fsaid: "As a council, we are committed
OL,16,Fto ensuring that vulnerable households
OL,17,Fget the help they need, especially
OL,18,Fduring these challenging times.
